6. New! Search on schwab.com
---------------------------------------------------------------- 
Now there's a fast and easy way to find the information you want 
on schwab.com. Our new search engine's capability goes beyond 
conventional search tools. You can ask a question or enter the 
action you want to take - in plain English - to get information
on investing and investment definitions, and access forms to
make customer service requests. 

For example: 

- What's the PE ratio, ROE and 52 week high for PG and Clorox? 
- How do I set up my account for automatic deposit? 
- Can I buy multiple stocks in one trade? 
- What is net asset value?

Let Search help you find what you need. Log in and try it today! 

Go to: 
http://schwab.ed10.net/ud/YVHZ/30NW/VLY9/36/046LS

