9. Take an Objective Look at Your Investment Strategy
and Portfolio  
---------------------------------------------------------------- 
You follow the week-to-week flow of the market, but what about 
the bigger picture? Is your investment strategy on track to 
meet your lifestyle goals? Are you saving enough for a secure 
retirement? 

For objective advice on these questions, schedule an
appointment  with a Schwab Investment Specialist today.

Together, you and your Schwab Investment Specialist can:

- Review your current investment plan and, if necessary,
reallocate  your assets based on your risk tolerance and
time horizon
- Explore new investment strategies
- Discuss estate planning, college planning, and retirement 
planning
- Identify tools and resources that can help you make more 
informed investment decisions

Call 888-838-0782 to set up an appointment.

